2 Kampamffamayr and Khemiari; Leaders in contemporary Arabic Literature
~~part 1- London, 1950.
3 د. محمد سامي البدراوي: المرجع السابق ص270.
Pierse cachih. Taha Hussein. His place in the Egyptian, Literary
